title: Spacious Classic Uptown 1 bdrm available Oct 1st!
map_address: Colfax Ave S near West 24th Street
posting_body: ['Classic and beautiful 1 bdrm, in 6 unit HISTORIC MANSION at 2313 Colfax Ave S.', 'Open and bright living space with gorgeous hardwood floors and woodwork throughout.', 'All walls will be painted an Antique White.', 'Beautiful pocket doors can divide living and dining rooms if desired.', 'Stately faux fireplace in living room and large built in buffet in kitchen/dining room.', 'Gas stove and dishwasher!', 'Large windows throughout to bring in the sunshine!', 'Large front porch for lounging on those amazing summer days!', 'A cozy bedroom and bathroom with shower and additional storage closet round out this great apartment!', "Excellent location in the heart of the Wedge, on busline, walk to The Wedge Co-op, Kowalski's,", 'restaurants, lakes, and coffee shops.', 'Available October 1st!', 'Heat, water, and trash are paid.', 'Off street parking for an additional charge when available.', 'Applicants must have good credit and references.', 'Please email us or call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a showing.']
